      %h1 How much does gold return?
      %p
        Gold has been performing very well over the decades in India. For example, over the last 5 years amidst all the uncertainties and economic turmoil, gold has appreciated by a fabulous 139.41%. As mentioned earlier, gold serves as a safe heaven. The more the uncertainty, the greater the appreciation you can expect.
